{"id": 1960, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得现在人们对“独立”的理解，哪些可能有偏差？", "description": "经济独立、情感独立、思想独立，在独立被受推崇的如今，有哪些可能跑偏的独立值得我们警惕，欢迎留言探讨。(图片来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 14491, "comment_count": 56, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171016175559WrKQ5XOYMmGSAdNz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-17T17:00:20Z", "questions": [{"id": 3137, "title": "你觉得现在人们对“独立”的理解，哪些可能有偏差？", "content": "你遇到过哪些对“独立”的理解可能有偏差？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 242189, "content": "经济独立：平时我的是我的，关键时刻爸妈的也是我的", "image": "img/option/option/20171017162405kZeu0hiMRUrvz9gq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242049, "content": "把情感独立等同于对爱情/亲情的冷处理，为了不依赖父母/伴侣而冷落对方", "image": "img/option/option/20171016180226YyPw6Jd7CMAsvQIg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242050, "content": "为了提高自尊而盲目自信，“我接受自己的全部，我就是这样”", "image": "img/option/option/20171016180448D3WqoEwNQMjAztvK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242051, "content": "认为大众都是乌合之众，拒绝讨论和交流", "image": "img/option/option/20171016180549vAVKugLe0QM7NI4T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242052, "content": "认为人格独立即“不在意他人的评价”，不顾他人地以自我为中心", "image": "img/option/option/20171016180810cHJBOp2URa8zu3XS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242053, "content": "把没什么要紧的特立独行当做思想独立，“我从不关心偶像，拒绝升级IOS11”", "image": "img/option/option/20171016181528qAlLtIJugvUroOcy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242054, "content": "把独当一面单纯理解为“自己做”，担心“麻烦别人”而不愿意团队合作", "image": "img/option/option/20171016180940Mw84IUWrZ17GTRso.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242055, "content": "固执己见，我可不能被说服了，否则就是“随大流”", "image": "img/option/option/20171016181021aCfNDQWKTotmdPUu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}